          <a class="btn primary" href={`mailto:${CONTACT}?subject=ModelPilot beta — repo invite`}>Request beta access →</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="#quickstart">2-minute quickstart</a>
        </div>
        <pre class="term"><span class="c"># guidance mode — your key, zero change to your traffic</span>
$ export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
$ modelpilot gateway --mode guidance --port 8400
<span class="c"># point one app at it:  ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8400</span>

  classification   <span class="g">→ would route to claude-haiku-4-5</span>   conf 0.85
  debugging        <span class="y">→ stays on claude-opus-4-8</span>         quality protected
  extraction       <span class="g">→ would route to claude-haiku-4-5</span>   conf 0.85
  ...
dashboard → autopilot would save <span class="g">48% of baseline</span> — switch when ready</pre>
