            <div class="demo-screen" id="mp-demo">

              <div class="scene on" data-scene="1">
                <div class="reqlog">
                  <div class="row"><span class="m">$</span> export ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8400 &nbsp;<span class="m"># the only change to your app</span></div>
                  <div class="row"><span class="m">$</span> modelpilot gateway --mode guidance --port 8400</div>
                  <div class="row"><span class="m"># measuring — nothing rerouted; your traffic is untouched</span></div>
                  <div class="row"><span class="m">POST /v1/messages</span> "Classify ticket: 'charged twice'" &nbsp;opus→<b>haiku</b> <span class="ok">0.86 ✓</span></div>
                  <div class="row"><span class="m">POST /v1/messages</span> "Write SQL: top accounts by MRR" &nbsp;opus→<b>haiku</b> <span class="ok">0.85 ✓</span></div>
                  <div class="row"><span class="m">POST /v1/messages</span> "Debug: workers double-process" &nbsp;opus→opus <span class="keep2">keep · hard</span></div>
                  <div class="row"><span class="m">POST /v1/messages</span> "Summarize this PR diff" &nbsp;opus→<b>haiku</b> <span class="ok">0.85 ✓</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="scene" data-scene="2">
                <div class="dashhead"><b>ModelPilot</b><span class="mode">guidance mode · localhost:8400/modelpilot/dashboard</span></div>
                <div class="convbox">
                  <div class="row h">READY TO SWITCH TO AUTOPILOT?</div>
                  <div class="row big">$312 you could save <small>— 41% of your Claude spend this week · ~$16k/yr</small></div>
                  <div class="row" style="color:var(--mut);font-size:.82rem;margin-top:6px">Only the routes we're confident in. Nothing rerouted yet — you're in guidance.</div>
                </div>
